00:09:03,892 --> 00:09:04,592
up to their stopping.

184
00:09:05,910 --> 00:09:13,918
We've extended the system to be sideways movement scuffs, and we use high-velocity vertical movement on characters to play

185
00:09:14,339 --> 00:09:15,600
procedural landing sounds.

186
00:09:16,721 --> 00:09:19,784
All of these are surface specific. We have something like

