00:09:19,804 --> 00:09:24,749
26-30 surfaces per game. And of course we extend this system into creature foots.

188
00:09:26,332 --> 00:09:32,154
A similar setup for cloth. Short samples based on bone distance and bone pass of knee and elbow.

189
00:09:33,435 --> 00:09:38,497
