00:10:22,575 --> 00:10:26,197
We have eight emitters, there's head, dialogue, chest,

205
00:10:26,717 --> 00:10:30,699
left and right hands, knee, and both feet.

206
00:10:30,959 --> 00:10:32,560
So the emitters are tracked at runtime,

