00:30:26,068 --> 00:30:28,190
to clean up the mix when the water was pumping,

484
00:30:28,290 --> 00:30:29,992
was high enough in level.

485
00:30:32,136 --> 00:30:36,319
Dialogue had its normal varied ducking on pretty much everything

