00:30:36,759 --> 00:30:38,801
to make it audible regardless of what was going on.

487
00:30:40,202 --> 00:30:42,323
And the explosions, similar to dialogue,

488
00:30:42,663 --> 00:30:44,525
ducked everything by a relatively high amount

489
00:30:45,065 --> 00:30:46,846
to make them feel bigger in the mix.

490
00:30:47,226 --> 00:30:48,267
So I hope you're all still with this.

491
00:30:50,428 --> 00:30:52,610
And atmospheres, they basically got ducked by everything.

